            <h2>Volunteer Opportunities</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Bike Repair Stations:</strong> Help with basic repairs at our community shops (no experience needed - we train!)</li>
                <li><strong>Mobile Repair Unit:</strong> Join our bike repair van that visits underserved neighborhoods</li>
                <li><strong>Youth Workshops:</strong> Teach bike maintenance to kids ages 10-16</li>
                <li><strong>Bike Tours:</strong> Lead guided cycling tours of city landmarks and hidden gems</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>Bike Sponsorship Program</h2>
            <p>For $150, you can sponsor a refurbished bike for someone in need. Sponsors receive:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Profile of the bike recipient (with their permission)</li>
                <li>"Sponsor" decal on the bike</li>
                <li>Invitation to our annual Bike Fair</li>
                <li>Tax receipt for your donation</li>
            </ul>
            
